<p>Current paid up members of the McNear gardens may access your personal information, including plot assignments, phone numbers and email address.  Members, including the board, may only use this information to communicate with you about McNear Gardens’ activities, such as upcoming meetings, pending subscriptions and community hours worked, and other pertinent information about the garden activities. We take this privilege very seriously and will address any member who abuses another members personal information in anyway, including revoking their access to the website or revoking their membership to the organization; You can flag your personal information as private in the “Personal Information” section of your account page in which case other members, excluding the officers of the board of directors, cannot access this information in any way. The board reserves the right to access your contact information to communicate with you about upcoming meetings, pending subscriptions and community hours worked, and other pertinent information about the garden activities at the boards discretion.</p>
<p>The McNear Community Garden board may send you occasional e-mails about McNear Garden Community Work Days, McNear Garden group meetings and information about your subscription and community hours logged. You can unsubscribe from these mailing in the “Personal Information” section of your account page.
